ng aggregation, given a request, as well as a number of ranking lists of offerings, one wants to generate a new ranking list of the offerings.  aTitle from PDF title page (viewed on November 19, 2014).  a44 0aRanking and selection (Statistics) 0aInformation retrieval. 0aNatural language processing (Computer science) 0aMachine learning. 0aSynthesis digital library of engineering and computer science. 0aSynthesis lectures on human language technologies ;v# 26.x1947-4059403University of Alberta Accessuhttp://dx.doi.org/10.2200/S00607ED2V01Y201410HLT026  hUAINzSYNTHDIG  aInternet AccesswLCc1i6742016-1001lINTERNETmUAINTERNETrYsYtE-RESOURCEu11/25/2014xE-BOOKzSYNTHDIG01ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n2008064030bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/18063505